citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process from 8:45AM to
9:30AM on 10/09/2015. A person at the facility wasn't sure if licensee had left for the day; I waited in case licensee
was still there but did not see him.

narrative:
2.126(b)                    REPEAT
ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process from 8:45AM to
9:30AM on 10/09/2015.  A person at the facility wasn't sure if licensee had left for the day; I waited in case licensee
was still there but did not see him.
